Groundstation tools for monitoring UAV telemetry

Dependencies:
 * libserial
     This is configured as a submodule of this repository,
     so if it is not available on your system then you need
     only do 
     $git submodule init && git submodule update 
     from the top of tree
 * python-osm-gps-map
     http://github.com/nzjrs/osm-gps-map
     This does not need to be installed system wide, you can just
     build it and update your PYTHONPATH accordingly
     $export PYTHONPATH=/path/to/osm/python/.libs
     
Run these like follows
./groundstation.py
./tools/console-serial-monitor.py
./tools/gui-serial-monitor.py
